Name: Titus
Owner: @emperortitusthethick
Summary: What is this big boy dreaming of? The answer may surprise you… or it may not… we don’t even know what he’s dreaming of. How could we? We can’t read minds. Comment what you think he’s dreaming of!
•
He eats small portions of healthy food and exercises!

node.text:
•
Name: Sally Cinnamon 
Owner: @kimberleyesmith 
Summary: Sally Cinnamon has a daily routine at night and she sticks to it. She will go to the McDonald’s drive through at 8pm and she must be driving out of there at 8:01pm. For every minute her order is late, she asks them to add an employee to the order…..you should hear the fear in their voice when she tells them what will happen.
•
Sally Cinnamon is on a diet trying to shed a few pounds!
